description:
The whole store and more, now at your fingertips.  

Our award-winning shopping app helps you save time and money.  

Shop anytime, anywhere
• Millions of items available with free delivery or store pickup.  
• Easily re-order favorite items purchased online or in-store with just a few taps.  
• Order, transfer, and track prescriptions and refills.  
• Find, create, and manage a baby registry.  
• Transfer money without the long wait or the paperwork with Express Money Services.  
• Free delivery on eligible orders $35 and up.

Smart in-store shopping   
• Save time shopping at your local Walmart with store assistant.  
• Use Walmart Pay for touch-free checkout. 
• Quickly locate items and Rollbacks with store maps.    
• Create and share shopping lists.

Fresh groceries and more  
• Choose grocery delivery or curbside pickup.  
• Reserve a time that best works for you.  
• We’ll do the grocery shopping.  
• No markups or hidden fees. 

Do Not Sell My Personal Information.
Please scroll down to the footer of our Privacy Policy below to find the "Do Not Sell My Personal Information" link
https://corporate.walmart.com/privacy-security

description:
Available today in Pittsburgh, Kansas City, and Vero Beach! 

Walmart InHome is a new delivery service that gets the to-dos done. InHome uses smart entry technology to deliver Walmart groceries, household essentials, and prescriptions ordered from the Walmart Grocery app or grocery.walmart.com right into your home. See if your address is eligible and sign up at inhome.walmart.com.  

How to use Walmart InHome: 

• Place your order in Walmart Grocery app (or grocery.walmart.com) and choose "InHome Delivery" at checkout 
• For prescriptions, place your order through the Walmart app's Pharmacy section and select "InHome" at checkout 

Key Features of the Walmart InHome app: 

• Track the status of your Walmart Grocery & Walmart Pharmacy orders delivered by InHome 
• Watch a video livestream of your orders getting delivered in the app or save for later viewing (up to a week after your delivery is completed) 
• Get notifications at every step of your delivery—including when your order is on its way to your house and when the delivery has finished 
• See the InHome delivery associate who'll deliver your groceries & prescriptions 

Do Not Sell My Personal Information

Please scroll down to the footer of our Privacy Policy below to find the "Do Not Sell My Personal Information" link https://corporate.walmart.com/privacy-security

description:
Our new ReliOn™ Life Patient Mobile App is a free tool for ReliOn™ meter users to track their blood sugar readings, activity, diet, and mood.

You choose what to log and how much detail to add. Add context to your logs with optional note details or share your blood glucose readings with your healthcare provider. Find patterns by digging deeper into your reading history to understand ways to adjust your diabetes management.

ReliOn™ Life is only compatible with the following ReliOn™ blood glucose meters: Premier BLU, Premier VOICE, Confirm, and Prime.

releaseNotes:
Prepare for the greatest challenge yet!
 
In your Deli/Bakery department, you will lead your team to success through multiple challenges. Can you keep the right amount of baked fresh foods to meet needs without wasting any? Can you nail timings and ensure your team is where they are supposed to be when they are supposed to be there?
 
Once you have mastered Deli/Bakery, you’ll be promoted to Assistant Store Manager to tackle coordinating a huge season: Thanksgiving and Black Friday. Help balance the day-to-day tasks to keep the store successful, and complete the work that needs to be done for Black Friday. While the timings are different than real life, the tasks and pressures are real!

description:
NTransit® is a quick and simple way for drivers to spend more time driving and less time waiting in line at a distribution center while ensuring the right freight get delivered at the right time.

Available Features
Proof of Delivery – With POD drivers can ensure that the right freight gets unloaded at the right Walmart store. The driver will have the ability to scan pallets as they are unloaded from the trailer and the app will keep track and notify the driver if any pallets that were scanned were not intended for that store.
NTransit is currently only available to drivers whose company has certified with Walmart.  If your company is not currently signed up please have them contact us at walmart.transportation.mobile@gmail.com .

description:
United Voice WorkIt is an app that provides United Voice members with answers to any workplace questions they have. Workers have direct access to the knowledge and information they need to be informed about their rights and entitlements - regardless of whether they’ve just clocked off at 2am, or about to walk into a meeting with management.
 
United Voice WorkIt has been trained on company policies, enterprise agreements, awards, and state and federal laws – so simply type in a question, and you’ll get the answer relevant to you (based on whether you’re casual or permanent, which department you work in, and who your direct employer is).
 
With United Voice WorkIt, users can access: 

Instant information. WorkIt empowers members by giving them access to instant, accurate information about their workplace – no matter where they are or what time it is, all through a simple chat interface or through searchable archives of previously asked questions
A community of peers. People are able to safely and securely chat in the chat rooms, helping to strategise around solutions, share knowledge and connect with others in their workplace
Alerts and news bulletins. Get up to date information on agreements, workplace changes, and United Voice events through your in app news section and push notifications

If you like WorkIt, please rate the app, like and share on Facebook and Instagram!
